{"tid":2411604,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"越南網吧變身Bitcoin礦場  8 張 RTX 3080 合體挖礦","createTime":"2021-02-17T12:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T03:24:18.000Z","uid":15564,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ade5ce26bb4afad0d3af1e11c431940db8d168c1","tid":2411604,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.videocardz.com/1/2021/02/Internet-Cafe-CryptoCurrency-Mining2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.videocardz.com%2F1%2F2021%2F02%2FInternet-Cafe-CryptoCurrency-Mining2.jpg&h=c5fd82a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信疫情下不少店家都難以維持生計，連越南網吧亦不例外。由於政府限制人潮聚集室內場所營業，因此有網吧改裝成加密貨幣礦場，更運用店內的 GeForce RTX 30 系列顯示卡改裝成機架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/148209454_2844953915777496_1338451001726825413_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F148209454_2844953915777496_1338451001726825413_o.jpg&h=cceb20df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南於 1 月底左右又爆發一波疫情，當地政府隨即限制網吧等人潮聚集室內場所營業，結果導致生意不繼。而店家為求生存更將網吧改裝成加密貨幣礦場，照片顯示，店家整合了店內所有電腦的顯示卡進行加密貨幣運算，，其中有機架結合了 8 張 GeForce RTX 3080 SG 顯示卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/146583848_2844953922444162_1621088317107753300_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F146583848_2844953922444162_1621088317107753300_o.jpg&h=86f3c68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/146583848_2844953922444162_1621088317107753300_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F146583848_2844953922444162_1621088317107753300_o.jpg&h=86f3c68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受疫情所迫之下，網吧店主無奈將店中的電腦改裝成加密貨幣礦場。而最諷刺的是，據悉由於疫情未減緩加上近日加密貨幣持續飆升，將這些 GeForce RTX 30 系列顯示卡改裝成加密貨幣礦場反而獲利更多，成為網吧店家的續命稻草。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://videocardz.com/newz/internet-cafes-are-transforming-into-cryptocurrency-mining-cafes-profits-are-higher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideocardz.com%2Fnewz%2Finternet-cafes-are-transforming-into-cryptocurrency-mining-cafes-profits-are-higher&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN23hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=1947ec17\" target=\"_blank\">https://videocardz.com/newz/internet-cafes-are-transforming-into-cryptocurrency-mining-cafes-profits-are-higher</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/16/vietnambitcoin/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F16%2Fvietnambitcoin%2Fnotebook%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN23hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=ee26e6b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/16/vietnambitcoin/notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"d29f563ba7a6719e08e3059fcca53f3c5c2afc2f","tid":2411604,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"香港啲網吧學佢咁轉型得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df13647651eb038dcdf816b4f40695c6ff700dbe","tid":2411604,"uid":123189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"比唔比得起電費呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde9d549347692fda29184a6fb7eaf2f727418a7","tid":2411604,"uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df13647651eb038dcdf816b4f40695c6ff700dbe","tid":2411604,"uid":123189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"比唔比得起電費呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"咁屌都要認清個事實<br />\n香港電費計<br />\n班礦佬大約都賺10蚊先比一至兩蚊電費<br />\n其他地方應該仲平"},{"pid":"9087a8c8f4e2f87536b0d38a43f05254b1d4fe41","tid":2411604,"uid":231725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"舊tesla免費差電<br />\n擺礦機入去<br />\n